<refsect1 id="libxklavier-desc"><title>&desc-tt;</title>
<para>
libxklavier is a utility library to make working with XKB easier. libxklavier
simplify XKB-related development and provide support for providing keyboard
selection at GDM and for gnome keyboard switching mechanism in the gnome desktop.
</para>
</refsect1>

